Hashes allows the ______ to get information quickly
Hashes are curly brackets to initialize

Best Vacation Sports for 
'Art' => Paris			:Art => Paris	
'Beach' => Rio			:Beach => Rio
'Nature' => Alaska		:Nature => Alaska	


best_vacation_spots['Beach'] returns Rio
best_vacation_spots['Nature'] returns Alaska
best_vacation_spots['Art'] returns Paris

